 /> <br />\n<br />\n炒滑蛋發嘅時候，筷子係唔會離開碗底，否則會將空氣打入，變左唔滑<br />\n<br />\n另外，油太多，咁多油，咩wok都唔痴啦。"},{"pid":"cca2b3bf875290768a5006d35b47dd06dfd5c249","tid":95601,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d344981cda778c71ef13df2afe5d0f50cfb4893f","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:25:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到似模似樣，聽發蛋聲就知未到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炒滑蛋發嘅時候，筷子係唔會離開碗底，否則會將空氣打入，變左唔滑<br />\n<br />\n另外，油太多，咁多油，咩wok都唔痴啦。</blockquote><br />\n師兄好似講到似模似樣咁wo，不過唔係話challenge你，理論既野唔可以當飯食話，你估宜家上chem? 好似你咁打蛋，炒出黎個效果唔會差得遠，宜家唔係整蛋糕呀細佬。同埋你話多油實唔痴，其實果度唔算多油，炒蛋唔痴獲既重點唔係多油，係要夠油就得，同埋隻獲要先燒紅，再落油朗獲，咁就唔會痴，唔好以為多油係萬能，炒碟牛河，如果唔識炒，多多油到痴到你仆街呀，小朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee691a0c33395186a5e5ef818241fbfc4e17e83","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n🍻"},{"pid":"768f05f8e0130dd704e50deadeb13495b7635ced","tid":95601,"uid":41605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"落雨天炒蛋得唔得"},{"pid":"d331091c8a67ddd749729c7499c1727c4a7b6605","tid":95601,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"Lin都唔識貼 罰你炒一碟比我<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g82Ne6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg82Ne6.gif&h=c6efedb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57b19d21b0c54b6a8fc66319e2a9b1468e4fecf2","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquot