r />\n師兄好似講到似模似樣咁wo，<span style=\"color: red;\">不過唔係話challenge你</span>，理論既野唔可以當飯食話，你估宜家上chem? 好似你咁打蛋，炒出黎個效果唔會差得遠，宜家唔係整蛋糕呀細佬。同埋你話多油實唔痴，其實果度唔算多油，炒蛋唔痴獲既重點唔係多油，係要夠油就得，同埋隻獲要先燒紅，再落油朗獲，咁就唔會痴，唔好以為多油係萬能，炒碟牛河，如果唔識炒，多多油到痴到你仆街呀，小朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你又要教人，指正你又唔接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋又係你影片入面話要多油，依加又唔同講法？"},{"pid":"4bb9c99cf05a79b2b7719bfc1b435a7172f26efd","tid":95601,"uid":12328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:12:58.000Z","msg":"巴打我買左蝦醬唔識整蝦醬炒飯啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caa9fbab0f94fbf3c5444315dd477d19aa21921","tid":95601,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到似模似樣，聽發蛋聲就知未到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炒滑蛋發嘅時候，筷子係唔會離開碗底，否則會將空氣打入，變左唔滑<br />\n<br />\n另外，油太多，咁多油，咩wok都唔痴啦。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z6qa8nrx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz6qa8nrx&h=f2f4338e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇&hellip;&hellip;好多空氣呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c073fbe323d4cd247c67b61c0c8c07b4a9f89f","tid":95601,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T18:04:23.000Z","msg":"點炒到澳牛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda008ceeb6f03a71f826109d1ce640f4e74518f","tid":95601,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T