aces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慢慢來，過年後得閒d會整 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c12821b0a2b9206efd649dcfe4de42c0922ebf","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講到似模似樣，聽發蛋聲就知未到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炒滑蛋發嘅時候，筷子係唔會離開碗底，否則會將空氣打入，變左唔滑<br />\n<br />\n另外，油太多，咁多油，咩wok都唔痴啦。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z6qa8nrx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz6qa8nrx&h=f2f4338e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇&hellip;&hellip;好多空氣呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打心水清，果然係煮得之人，唔似得有d人為challenge而chanallenge, 話聽聲就知我點打蛋，我話佢講句野我就知佢唔識煮野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22aa453ed48c13c24c15e70c4c0de5077348c3c","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個已經學似巴打咁炒<br />\n不過唔會燒咁耐<br />\n同埋唔會熄火等<br />\n一樣咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆成日炒但都係好難食<br />\n煮野食係咪真係講天份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n天份係其次，興趣最重要，當你中意煮野，就會有要求，就會點都要做好先安樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a2fc512bbf28fc713a8b1331e087ecc3e00d97","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:17:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打可唔可以整麻婆豆腐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝支持 😊"},{"pid":"9b1f766d111181baddb5874182c36c738ca68cf0","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就來俾樓主搞到買生鐵鑊</blockquote><br />\n好便，係開獲要少少夫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17dc43883d688f8a32db4fc7ff92d94cb363f1fe","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇機會教下魚香茄子</blockquote><br />\n可以一試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7bee3f3d9c4a28a2c64522a7af98783764b385","tid":95601,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:19:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講到似模似樣，聽發蛋聲就知未到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炒滑蛋發嘅時候，筷子係唔會離開碗底，否則會將空氣打入，變左唔滑<br />\n<br />\n另外，油太多，咁多油，咩wok都唔痴啦。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z6qa8nrx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz6qa8nrx&h=f2f4338e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇&hellip;&hellip;好多空氣呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打心水清，果然係煮得之人，唔似得有d人為challenge而chanallenge, 話聽聲就知我點打蛋，我話佢講句野我就知佢唔識煮野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪打到唔起泡就靚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識煮野食 淨係識煮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874b4032266f92fb6815c9d06018c3dcb2cd48da","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點炒到澳牛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己炒唔洗受氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b24db9c7c6f00aba54693e2e9782c7385bc1fe1","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講到似模似樣，聽發蛋聲就知未到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炒滑蛋發嘅時候，筷子係唔會離開碗底，否則會將空氣打入，變左唔滑<br />\n<br />\n另外，油太多，咁多油，咩wok都唔痴啦。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z6qa8nrx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz6qa8nrx&h=f2f4338e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇&hellip;&hellip;好多空氣呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打心水清，果然係煮得之人，唔似得有d人為challenge而chanallenge, 話聽聲就知我點打蛋，我話佢講句野我就知佢唔識煮野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪打到唔起泡就靚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識煮野食 淨係識煮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實你唔係蒸水蛋，又唔係整蛋糕，真係冇咩所謂。炒蛋黎講，少少泡可以接受，最緊要打得勻，先係重點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e3085efcc22b84f05af38c2f870fa19c5c56d2","tid":95601,"uid":33607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:22:52.000Z","msg":"如果加奶<br />\n無鮮奶加維他d牛奶飲品得唔得sosad"},{"pid":"3fc0d1d0f24bb2f639932abf2be7bf239eecaa8f","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果加奶<br />\n無鮮奶加維他d牛奶飲品得唔得sosad</blockquote><br />\n效果冇咁好。我自己唔太喜歡加奶，因為加左奶果種滑我覺得唔太自然，而奶味又會遮蓋蛋味，純粹個人意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef6dffefed1dddc6bdf9a4094c7fdf59f8e93a5","tid":95601,"uid":51108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:37:20.000Z","msg":"易潔鑊係咪一樣要燒紅隻鑊先？<br />\n<br />\n同埋巴打有冇茶餐紅汁receipe呀？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61383bc44fadb01a75f9cefa8558b4c672c8b45","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>易潔鑊係咪一樣要燒紅隻鑊先？<br />\n<br />\n同埋巴打有冇茶餐紅汁receipe呀？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n易潔獲一般受唔到高溫，所以不能白獲燒紅，要先落油，用中火燒到油開始出煙就可炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2455e88befb92c3b3e470e5d7d3d23a3d420a570","tid":95601,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T00:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>易潔鑊係咪一樣要燒紅隻鑊先？<br />\n<br />\n同埋巴打有冇茶餐紅汁receipe呀？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n易潔獲一般受唔到高溫，所以不能白獲燒紅，要先落油，用中火燒到油開始出煙就可炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n汁既receipt可能過左小菜系列先出，請諒解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}